REPORTER: The
Japanese government

00:03:04.070 --> 00:03:06.890
has noted that whaling has long
been a part of their culture

00:03:06.890 --> 00:03:08.890
and acknowledge that they
would likely continue,

00:03:08.890 --> 00:03:10.460
despite the controversy.

00:03:10.460 --> 00:03:12.835
NARRATOR: And don't forget to
